On the other hand, the document sets out a number of general strategic objectives related to immigration, such as: promoting legal migration, more rigorous control of the legality of third-country nationals' headquarters in Romania and the proper application of removal and restrictive measures, improving the national asylum system.
The national strategy shall also include specific objectives relevant to the transposition and implementation of the general strategic objectives.
